brainbox/
│
├── src/
│   ├── App.js
│   ├── index.js
│   │
│   ├── Components/
│   │   ├── Navbar.js           → Navigation bar for the app.
│   │   ├── Subject.js          → Displays a single subject card with progress and button.
│   │   ├── Subject.css         → Styles for Subject.js component.
│   │   ├── Progress.js         → Renders the animated progress bar.
│   │   ├── Progress.css        → Styles for the progress bar.
│   │   ├── ChecklistPage.js    → Checklist for each subject, updates progress when items are checked.
│   │   │
│   │   └── data/
│   │       ├── mysubjects.js   → Base array of all subjects with studied and total hours.
│   │       └── subjectData.js  → Imports data from mysubjects.js and provides it to App.js.
│   │
│   ├── App.css                 → General app styling.
│   └── main.jsx                → Vite entry point; renders <App /> inside the DOM.
│
├── package.json                → Project dependencies and scripts.
├── README.md                   → Project documentation.
└── node_modules/               → Installed npm dependencies.

